{"type": "article", "id": 2252, "title": "辛普森 × 匡威联名款", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-08T17:43:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222313Veq9FCKb2zBRxXOf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t《辛普森一家》的 25 周年庆祝活动持续迎来与各品牌的联名作品，在印上 Nike 和 Adidas 鞋以及 GIVENCHY 的套装后，这次，它们又携手匡威发布全新 2014 秋冬系列，所有标志性的主角形象被印在 All Star 系列鞋款上，鞋舌上醒目的写着 The Simpsons 的字样。该系列提供低帮、高帮两种鞋款，有黑、白、粉三色可选，预计将在 9 月中旬正式发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222311af0yJFDevBg9hSkN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222311pKisS8W1hObELCJf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222312OlyeW3DIhXx0p8fK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222312wuXSjGi5HqfnadND.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}